    "value": "[{\"name\":\"Melbourne Paragliding\",\"logo\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://www.melbourneparagliding.com\",\"markdown\":\"Melbourne's premier paragliding school offering **tandem flights**, pilot training courses, and equipment sales. Whether you're a first-timer looking for the thrill of flight or an aspiring pilot ready to earn your wings, Melbourne Paragliding has you covered with experienced instructors and breathtaking coastal launch sites.\"},{\"name\":\"Bruce Agnew Photography\",\"logo\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://www.bruceagnew.com\",\"markdown\":\"Capturing the beauty of flight from above and below. Bruce specialises in **aerial and landscape photography**, documenting the paragliding community with stunning imagery. From action shots on launch to sweeping coastal panoramas, his work showcases the magic of free flight.\"}]"
